  <li>
    <p>In the Project Properties, navigate to Debug tab and hit the â€œDeleteâ€ button next to the Profile. When you hit the Delete button, the Profile that shows â€œIIS Expressâ€ will change to â€œTestAPIâ€ &amp; Launch will also change to â€œProjectâ€. We did this so that when we run this project, it runs as a console application. Why? Because for a Web API, you donâ€™t have a User Interface to work with.
<img src="https://abhisheksubbusite.s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/images/project-profile.png" alt="Project Profile" /></p>
