  <li>
    <p>So, change the URL to â€œhttps://localhost:5001/api/userâ€ and hit Enter. You will see the data with â€œnameâ€ property and â€œTest Nameâ€ value (exactly as we configured in the Controller code). Excellent progress till now.</p>

