  <li>
    <p>Now, we are ready to configure Swagger in this â€œTestAPIâ€ project. Close the browser window and the command window. This stops the project from running. In the project in Visual Studio, right click on â€œTestAPIâ€ project and choose â€œManage NuGet Packagesâ€ option</p>

    <p><img src="https://abhisheksubbusite.s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/images/manage-nuget.png" alt="Manage Nuget" /></p>
